caption.title: Maximum likelihood tree of the sequences included in the detected east Andalusian lineages (n = 234), together with the most closely related HIV-1 sequences from GenBank.
caption.p: Tip labels are depicted in blue for the east Andalusian sequences (and indicate the sampling date and region) and in black for the GenBank sequences (and indicate subtype, country, accession number and sampling date). Lineages are highlighted.
